<h2 id="peer-reviewed-publications">Peer-reviewed publications</h2>

<div class="message">
<span style="color:Maroon">Conference papers</span> |
<span style="color:Black">Journal papers</span> |
<span style="color:Green">Workshop papers/Posters</span> |
<span style="color:Blue">Patents</span> 
