<h2 class="bibliography">2019</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="icon-comsnets">Hamed Rezaei, Muhammad Usama Chaudhry, Hamidreza Almasi, and Balajee Vamanan, “<b>ICON: Incast Congestion Control using Packet Pacing in Datacenter Networks</b>,” in <i>(to appear) Proceedings of the International Conference on Communication Systems and Networks (COMSNETS)</i>, 2019.</span>   </li>
<li><span id="som-poster">Shih-Chang Hung, Nick Iliev, Balajee Vamanan, and Amit Ranjan Trivedi, “<b>Self-Organizing Maps-based Flexible and High-Speed Packet Classification in Software Defined Networking</b>,” in <i>(to appear) Proceedings of the International Conference on VLSI Design and Embedded Systems (VLSID)</i>, 2019.</span>   </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2018</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="slytherin-icccn">Hamed Rezaei, Mojtaba Malekpourshahraki, and Balajee Vamanan, “<b>Slytherin: Dynamic, Network-assisted Prioritization of Tail Packets in Datacenter Networks</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the International Conference on Computer Communications and Networks (ICCCN)</i>, 2018, pp. 1–9.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/slytherin-icccn.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/slytherin-icccn.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li>
<li><span id="dns">John Kristoff, Balajee Vamanan, and Chris Kanich, “<b>DNS Inconsistency</b>,” in <i>ICANN DNS Symposium</i>, 2018.</span>   </li>
<li><span id="blitz-poster">Jaichen Xue, Muhammad Usama Chaudhry, Balajee Vamanan, T. N. Vijaykumar, and Mithuna Thottethodi, “<b>Fast Congestion Control in RDMA-based Datacenter Networks</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the SIGCOMM Posters and Demos</i>, 2018.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/blitz-poster.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/blitz-poster.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li>
<li><span id="feed">Mojtaba Malekpourshahraki and Balajee Vamanan, “<b>FEED: Fast end-to-end ECN mark delivery with early congestion control response</b>,” in <i>Greater Chicago Area Systems Research Workshop (GCASR)</i>, 2018.</span>   </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2017</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="hydra-comsnets">Yiyang Chang, Ashkan Rezaei, Balajee Vamanan, Jahangir Hasan, Sanjay Rao, and T.N. Vijaykumar, “<b>Hydra: Leveraging Functional Slicing for Efficient Distributed SDN Controllers</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the International Conference on Communication Systems and Networks (COMSNETS)</i>, 2017, pp. 251–258.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/hydra-comsnets.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/hydra-comsnets.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li>
<li><span id="icon">Hamed Rezaei, Muhammad Usama Chaudhry, and Balajee Vamanan, “<b>ICON: Incast Tolerant Congestion Control to Improve Latency Tail and Throughput</b>,” in <i>Greater Chicago Area Systems Research Workshop (GCASR)</i>, 2017.</span>   </li>
<li><span id="patent3">Balajee Vamanan, T.N. Vijaykumar, and Mithuna Thottethodi, “<b>Receiver-directed Computer Network Congestion Control System</b>,” <i>US Patent 62701 filed</i>. 2017.</span>   </li>
<li><span id="hydra-lncs">Yiyang Chang, Ashkan Rezaei, Balajee Vamanan, Jahangir Hasan, Sanjay Rao, and T. N. Vijaykumar, “<b>Exploring Functional Slicing in the Design of Distributed SDN Controllers</b>,” <i>Lecture Notes in Computer Science (LNCS)</i>, 2017.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/hydra-lncs.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/hydra-lncs.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2016</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="crosslayer">Balajee Vamanan, “<b>Cross-Layer Optimizations between Network and Computer in Online Services</b>,” in <i>Greater Chicago Area Systems Research Workshop (GCASR)</i>, 2016.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/crosslayer.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/crosslayer.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2015</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="timetrader">Balajee Vamanan, Hamza Bin Sohail, Jahangir Hasan, and T.N. Vijaykumar, “<b>TimeTrader: Exploiting Latency Tail to Save Datacenter Energy for Online Search</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the International Symposium on Microarchitecture (MICRO)</i>, 2015.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/timetrader.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/timetrader.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li>
<li><span id="timethief">Balajee Vamanan, Hamza Bin Sohail, Jahangir Hasan, and T.N. Vijaykumar, “<b>TimeThief: Leveraging Network Variability to Save Datacenter Energy in On-line Data-Intensive Applications</b>,” in <i>Workshop on Architectures and Systems for Big Data (ASBD), co-located with ISCA</i>, 2015.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/timethief.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/timethief.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2014</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="flowbender">Abdul Kabbani, Balajee Vamanan, Jahangir Hasan, and Fabien Duchene, “<b>FlowBender: Flow-level Adaptive Routing for Improved Latency and Throughput in Datacenter Networks</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the ACM International Conference on Emerging Networking Experiments and Technologies (CoNEXT)</i>, 2014.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/flowbender.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/flowbender.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2013</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="patent1">Balajee Vamanan, Tukaram Methar, Mrudula Kanuri, and Sreenivas Krishnan, “<b>Processing of Read Requests in a Memory Controller using Prefetch Mechanism</b>,” <i>US Patent 8,489,851</i>. 2013.</span>   </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2012</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="d2tcp">Balajee Vamanan, Jahangir Hasan, and T.N. Vijaykumar, “<b>Deadline-aware Datacenter TCP (D2TCP)</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the ACM SIGCOMM Conference on Applications, Technologies, Architectures, and Protocols for Computer Communication (SIGCOMM)</i>, 2012.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/d2tcp.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/d2tcp.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li>
<li><span id="patent2">Tukaram Shankar Methar, Balajee Vamanan, and Sreenivas Krishnan, “<b>Command Latency Reduction and Command Bandwidth Maintenance in a Memory Circuit</b>,” <i>US Patent 8,261,121</i>. 2012.</span>   </li></ol>
<h2 class="bibliography">2011</h2>
<ol class="bibliography"><li><span id="treecam">Balajee Vamanan and T.N. Vijaykumar, “<b>TreeCAM: Decoupling Updates and Lookups in Packet Classification</b>,” in <i>Proceedings of the ACM International Conference on Emerging Networking Experiments and Technologies (CoNEXT)</i>, 2011.</span>  <a href="/~balajee/papers/treecam.pdf">[Paper]</a>   <a href="/~balajee/papers/treecam.pdf.pptx"> [Slides]</a>  </li></ol>
